BOOT      | 0       1000    1000    | 0         4096     4096     | 0         4        4      |
OTA_1     | 1000    78000   79000   | 4096      491520   495616   | 4         480      484    | 8000   32768   32 
OTA_2     | 81000   78000   F9000   | 528384    491520   1019904  | 516       480      996    | 2000   8192    8 
